Nice hotpot experience, value for money!

Came here at night for the hotpot and soup rice. Food are average, I would say slightly over price. The thing I particularly enjoyed is the Coconut Chicken Soup base, very rich in texture without being too salty. I may not recommend the sliced fish, portion is relatively little.
new restaurant serving hotpot with chicken, the ingredients is fresh which make the hotpot tasty, the price is fair
Great food, friendly staff and very reasonable price. I would come time after time

result.name: 頭啖湯

reviews.text: 上週五我們一班人用了openrice優惠券去吃晚餐（6-8時），椰子雞湯非常香濃好味又足料，其他材料可以有半價，也很新鮮，尤其安格斯牛。香茜牛丸和麻辣牛丸非常彈牙又惹味! 有個戴眼鏡的經理服務滿分，常幫我們添湯、拍照、招呼也非常細心周到。值得再來!😀
麻辣雞煲， 椰子雞湯底 真好味！

夜晚打邊爐價錢貴，蚌類食材唔新鮮，100蚊一碟細牛肩肉得7片，肉質水準非常一般，絕對唔值此價錢。依間鋪都第一次俾我試到魚蛋質感既黑椒牛丸，埋單3個人600幾，食物質數絕對比200內一位既火鍋放題差！
唯一可取係湯底比較好，但湯底好既打邊爐… 絕對唔係得依間。
Very good coconut 🥥 chicken 🐓 soup base!🤩 Beef 🥩 is great too. 😍Other food is just so so😕. Environment may be a bit shabby ☹️
